Combine the two square–root factors:

\[
\frac{\sqrt{75q^{5}}}{\sqrt{108q}}
      =\sqrt{\frac{75q^{5}}{108q}}
      =\sqrt{\frac{75}{108}\,q^{5-1}}
      =\sqrt{\frac{25}{36}\,q^{4}}.
\]

